data.description: Absolutely gorgeous 2 story pool home!   The lower landing of this this beautiful home has a spacious living room with tile flooring, formal family room/dining area with fireplace and tile flooring, 1 bedroom with a bathroom. Kitchen with tile flooring, center island, white tile counter tops and recessed lighting with a sliding door walk out the backyard.  This upper landing of this home features 4 spacious bedrooms including a main suite with 2 bathrooms, and a spacious loft. Main suite is spacious with own main bathroom which has a dual vanity, sunken bath, shower with glass doors and a walk-in closet.  The backyard is fully fenced and has an inground pool and jacuzzi, it has a covered concrete patio with ceiling fans.  Other amenities are indoor laundry room, Plantation shutters downstairs, front porch, 3 car attached garage, RV parking area.  Situated in a great location, close to schools, shops, entertainment, freeways and golf courses. This will not last.
